&lt;p&gt;
	This is an extension of &lt;a href=&quot;http://xy-kao.com/sandbox/led-matrix/&quot;&gt;controlling led matrices&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	The display is made of 12 matrices arranged in a 3:4 aspect ratio for a total of 768 LEDs. Like in the tutorial, the rows are controlled with 16-bit multiplexers and the columns with LED drivers, except that there are two of each.&lt;/p&gt;
